column2: SELECT s.specObjID, s.ra, s.dec, s.z, s.class, s.zWarning, s.snMedian, el.ra1, el.dec1, starforming.logMass, passive.logMass, pca.mstellar_median into mydb.MyTable_# from mydb.ell_galaxies2 as el CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestSpecObjEq (el.ra1, el.dec1, #) AS near JOIN SpecObjAll as s ON s.specObjID = near.specObjID JOIN stellarMassPassivePort passive ON passive.specObjID = near.specObjID JOIN stellarMassStarformingPort starforming ON starforming.specObjID = near.specObjID JOIN stellarMassPCAWiscM1# pca ON pca.specObjID = near.specObjID WHERE s.snMedian > = # AND s.class = # AND s.zWarning = #
